{
  "circuit": {
    "description": "8-bit voltage-mode R-2R ladder DAC. Each bit has a manual SPDT built from two SPST switches (Shi, Slo). Shi closed + Slo open = bit is 1 (arm to VREF). Shi open + Slo closed = bit is 0 (arm to GND). Vout = (code / 256) * VREF. R = 10k, 2R = 20k. Toggle Shi_i and Slo_i as a complementary pair per bit.",
